        <!--Main Content-->
        <div class="main-container">
            <h1>Welcome to STOL</h1>
            <h3>What is STOL?</h3>
            <p>STOL is a smart and easy-to-use web application that allows users to store and manage large files, <b>for free!</b></p>
            <h3>How does it work?</h3>
            <p>Behind the scenes, the application implements a very clever arhitecture that takes advantage of numerous cloud-storage services, such as Dropbox, 
                Google Drive and Microsoft OneDrive.</p>
            <h3>Who created STOL?</h3>
            <p>The application was created by 3 students from the Faculty Of Computer Science in Iasi as their final project for the Web Technologies subject. <br>
                For more information please feel free to visit the <a href="#" class="ref">About Us</a> page.
            </p>
            <h3>How can I use STOL?</h3>
            <p>It's all very simple! To start using the application you can easily register or log in with an existing account.<br>
                After that, everything should be made very easy by our beginner-friendly user interface!<br>
                For any questions left unanswered, please visit our <a href="#" class="ref">F.A.Q.</a> page.
            </p>
            <h3>Like what you read?</h3>
            <div class="button-container">
                <a href="./mainPage.html" class="start-button">Start using the app</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <!--End of Main Content-->
        <!--Footer-->
        <%- include ('../partials/footer.ejs') %>
        <!--End of Footer-->
